HEADWORD: Monarchal
<hw>Mo*nar"chal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to a
monarch; suiting a monarch; sovereign; regal; imperial.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Satan, whom now transcendent glory raised⟦br⟧
